<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

    <title>Eclipse Chronicles - Main Menu</title>

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
</head>

<body>

    <header>
        <h1>Eclipse Chronicles</h1>
        <p>A fantasy adventure awaits beyond the darkness.</p>
    </header>


    <nav>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="#start">Start Game</a></li>
            <li><a href="#features">Features</a></li>
            <li><a href="#about">About</a></li>
        </ul>
    </nav>


    <main>

        <section class="hero">

            <img src="images/background.jpg" 
                 alt="Fantasy landscape representing the game world">

            <div class="hero-text">

                <h2>Enter the Forgotten Realm</h2>

                <p>
                    Explore a mysterious world filled with ancient kingdoms,
                    powerful enemies, and unforgettable stories.
                </p>

                <a class="button" href="#start">
                    Begin Adventure
                </a>

            </div>

        </section>



        <section id="features" class="cards">

            <h2>Game Features</h2>


            <div class="card-container">

                <article class="card">

                    <h3>Explore</h3>

                    <p>
                        Discover hidden locations and uncover the secrets
                        of a forgotten civilization.
                    </p>

                </article>



                <article class="card">

                    <h3>Battle</h3>

                    <p>
                        Master combat abilities and defeat powerful enemies.
                    </p>

                </article>



                <article class="card">

                    <h3>Choices</h3>

                    <p>
                        Make decisions that influence your journey and ending.
                    </p>

                </article>

            </div>

        </section>




        <section id="about" class="about">

            <h2>About This Interface</h2>

            <p>
                This menu design combines dark fantasy visuals with modern
                game interface elements. The goal is to create a clear,
                immersive experience for players.
            </p>


            <h3>Main Menu Options</h3>

            <ul>

                <li>Continue Adventure</li>

                <li>New Game</li>

                <li>Settings</li>

                <li>Exit</li>

            </ul>


        </section>


    </main>



    <footer>

        <p>
            Created for Web Design Project 2
        </p>

        <p>
            Visit 
            <a href="https://www.nintendo.com" target="_blank">
                Nintendo
            </a>
            for game inspiration.
        </p>

    </footer>


</body>

</html>
